# Runtime event-log binary mirror (regenerable from factory-events.jsonl by
# honker_relay on start). The JSONL stays tracked as the audit trail; the
# 1MB+ SQLite mirror churns every commit and adds no source value (P17).
frames/factory-events.sqlite
